Package: hypermaze
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, hypermaze-data (=${source:Version})
Description: 3D maze like puzzle where you have to get a "string" through a "maze"
 For more explanations run the puzzle or for information about hypermazes in
 general see http://www.astrolog.org/labyrnth/hypermaz.htm. A tutorial and a
 level generator are included.

Package: hypermaze-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: architecture independent data for hypermaze
 Textures, models, sounds and example levels for hypermaze
